><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DOctal&amp;action=
=3Dedit&amp;section=3D19" title=3D"Edit section: Fractions"><span>edit</spa=
n></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
